# Token-only theming

To preserve the template style system:

- Prefer changing brand look by adjusting tokens in `tailwind.config.js` (colors/fonts/backgroundImage).
- Avoid introducing new one-off hex colors, custom inline styles, or new CSS rules for theming.

## Repo references (examples)
- Theme tokens: `tailwind.config.js` (e.g. `colors.coral-red`, `colors.slate-gray`)
- Shared layout utilities: `src/index.css` (`padding*`, `max-container`, `info-text`)

## Token stability
- Keep existing token names stable (e.g. `coral-red`, `slate-gray`) unless explicitly requested.
- If a rename is required, do it as a single coordinated change and update all usages.
